{"tid":1197660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連星期三罷一日工都唔敢既 你都唔洗再出黎抗爭","createTime":"2019-06-10T04:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T05:50:34.000Z","uid":60123,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe01d7294655116a360d0e3aefbb424cedb0d0d3","tid":1197660,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"遊行 大家試過<br />\n佔領 大家都試過<br />\n做呢D野根本係威脅唔到政府<br />\n大家唔想自己流血 我明<br />\n大家唔想自己坐監 我都明<br />\n<br />\n依家搞罷工 已經唔洗流血 唔洗坐監 最多冇份工<br />\n但連失去份工都驚過失去香港 咁你攬住份工過世 我唔阻你<br />\n大家要明白 公司冇人係冇得做落去 <br />\n你老闆知佢D人唔番工 一撚定係佢驚多過你驚<br />\n或者炒人唔難 但請番新人黎再重新教過晒係好難<br />\n若然你老闆係真係炒既話 呢D咁既老闆 你仲想跟?你做人係咁冇尊嚴?<br />\n<br />\n工作固然係大家既職責 之不過<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">守護香港</span></strong>係更重要既職責 係我地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人既使命</span></strong><br />\n你做得香港人 你就有份要保護香港 依件事係責無旁貸 唔好諗住可以卸膊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif?ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif%3Fssl%3D1&h=698e13c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.12 全港罷工罷課罷市</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"96ecfb44bb5d47476d96b0cc7f6dd5d8c8f882c8","tid":1197660,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4efac6456c58f323664a98fb2aa12e6be95fc3b","tid":1197660,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35b1e439f41fe1fc4afa3f23748541778c40180f","tid":1197660,"uid":5065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:50:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d23d84a1337b3fc0651c14e1a7750f3fb6bbad7","tid":1197660,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"878ab00f84e0328884a7f8206aeeec817fb7137b","tid":1197660,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T0